# car
# Converted from the hardcoded arrays in CarMesh.cs - Stunt Car Racer: The Sharp Kind
# The visible car shape from the original Car.cpp (CreateCarInVB): four flat
# wheel quads and a wedge-shaped body. Materials are resolved via CarPalette
# (Track.ScrBaseColour + offset), not an mtllib.

